data.description: Welcome to 531 E Winona Ave. Located in the Norwod Boro's. As you drive up to your off street parking with ample space. Walk into this beautiful livingroom with 9ft ceilings and  updated paint with new light fixture.  Kitchen has been painted as well to give a more modern look.  You will find in the basement space for the whole family .  Has been remodeled with barn doors to add style. The back yard has space for entertaining and has an above ground pool that is staying. (as is). Back upstairs you find an updated cosmetics in the bathroom paint and light feature. Followed by 2 bedrooms and 1full bathroom on the 1st floor with good space. Walk up to the 2nd level and you find 2 more bedrooms and 1 full bathroom painted.  Seller has painted the house and updated all the light fixtures. Has been an area sought after! Too much to fall in love with this home. Put a Yes on it! Possible Grants available!  Professional pictures will be coming soon!  The seller will sell some furniture pieces and TV's for right price.
